###  http://onto.vaimee.com/agora#bulkDensity
:bulkDensity rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty ;
             rdfs:subPropertyOf owl:topDataProperty ;
             rdfs:domain :SoilFeature ;
             rdfs:range xsd:decimal .


